pear-pear.horde.org/horde_text_filter_cs.name: pear-pear.horde.org/horde_text_filter_csstidy
pear-pear.horde.org/horde_text_filter_cs.description: The Horde_Text_Filter_Csstidy:: class provides the PHP-based library needed to perform optimization/compression on CSS code. It is provided in a separate package as the code is under the GPLv2 license instead of the LGPLv2 license used for the Text_Filter class.
